#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:1
msgid "UCM Store Deployment Guide"
msgstr "UCM存储部署指南"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:3
msgid "Why Use UCM"
msgstr "为何使用UCM"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:5
msgid ""
"Unified Cache Manager (UCM) provides an external KV-cache storage layer "
"designed for prefix-caching scenarios in vLLM/vLLM-Ascend. Unlike KV "
"Pooling, which expands prefix-cache capacity only by aggregating device "
"memory and therefore remains limited by HBM/DRAM size and lacks "
"persistence, UCM decouples compute from storage and adopts a tiered "
"design. Each node uses local DRAM as a fast cache, while a shared "
"backend—such as NFS, 3FS, or enterprise-grade storage—serves as the "
"persistent KV store."
msgstr ""
"统一缓存管理器（UCM）为vLLM/vLLM-"
"Ascend中的前缀缓存场景提供外部KV缓存存储层。与仅通过聚合设备内存扩展前缀缓存容量、因此仍受HBM/DRAM大小限制且缺乏持久性的KV池化不同，UCM将计算与存储解耦，采用分层设计。每个节点使用本地DRAM作为快速缓存，而共享后端（如NFS、3FS或企业级存储）则作为持久化KV存储。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:7
msgid "**Key benefits of using UCM:**"
msgstr "**使用UCM的主要优势：**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:9
msgid ""
"**Breaks Device Memory Capacity Limits**: Traditional prefix caching is "
"constrained by HBM/DRAM size. UCM removes this ceiling by offloading KV "
"cache to external storage, enabling cache capacity to scale with the "
"storage system rather than with compute resources."
msgstr "**突破设备内存容量限制**：传统前缀缓存受限于HBM/DRAM大小。UCM通过将KV缓存卸载到外部存储来消除这一上限，使缓存容量随存储系统而非计算资源扩展。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:11
msgid ""
"**Persistent and Reliable KV Cache**: UCM provides durable KV cache "
"storage, ensuring that cached prefix blocks survive across service "
"restarts, instance failures, or scheduling migrations. This is critical "
"for production-grade inference systems."
msgstr "**持久可靠的KV缓存**：UCM提供持久的KV缓存存储，确保缓存的prefix块在服务重启、实例故障或调度迁移后仍然存活。这对生产级推理系统至关重要。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:13
msgid ""
"**Multi-Scenario Acceleration**: UCM not only supports prefix caching but"
" also offers training-free sparse attention methods (e.g., GSA, "
"CacheBlend) for handling extremely long sequence inference tasks. "
"Additionally, UCM provides PD disaggregation solutions based on storage-"
"compute separation architecture, enabling flexible management of "
"heterogeneous computing resources."
msgstr "**多场景加速**：UCM不仅支持前缀缓存，还提供免训练的稀疏注意力方法（如GSA、CacheBlend）用于处理超长序列推理任务。此外，UCM基于存算分离架构提供PD分离解决方案，实现异构计算资源的灵活管理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:15
msgid ""
"**Significant Performance Improvement**: When integrated with vLLM, UCM "
"achieves **3-10x reduction** in inference latency across various "
"scenarios, including multi-turn dialogue and long-context reasoning "
"tasks. Benchmarks show up to **8x improvement in TTFT** for prefix "
"caching scenarios."
msgstr "**显著性能提升**：与vLLM集成后，UCM在多轮对话和长上下文推理等多种场景下实现**3-10倍**推理延迟降低。基准测试显示，在前缀缓存场景中TTFT提升高达**8倍**。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:17
msgid "How UCM Works"
msgstr "UCM工作原理"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:19
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:21
msgid ""
"UCM adopts a **centralized architecture** for KV cache management, "
"constructing a three-tier cache hierarchy:"
msgstr "UCM采用**集中式架构**进行KV缓存管理，构建三级缓存层次结构："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:27
msgid "This three-tier design enables:"
msgstr "这种三级设计实现了："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:29
msgid "**HBM (Tier 1)**: Fastest access for active inference computation"
msgstr "**HBM（第1层）**：为活跃推理计算提供最快访问"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:30
msgid ""
"**DRAM (Tier 2)**: High-speed local cache for frequently accessed KV "
"blocks"
msgstr "**DRAM（第2层）**：为频繁访问的KV块提供高速本地缓存"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:31
msgid ""
"**Storage Backend (Tier 3)**: Persistent storage layer including local "
"SSD, NFS-mounted storage, or dedicated systems like 3FS for unlimited "
"capacity scaling"
msgstr "**存储后端（第3层）**：持久化存储层，包括本地SSD、NFS挂载存储或3FS等专用系统，实现无限容量扩展"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:33
msgid ""
"UCM chose the centralized approach (similar to DeepSeek's 3FS) over "
"decentralized designs for several reasons:"
msgstr "UCM选择集中式方法（类似于DeepSeek的3FS）而非去中心化设计，原因如下："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:35
msgid ""
"**Simplicity**: Avoids complex affinity scheduling required in "
"decentralized architectures"
msgstr "**简单性**：避免了去中心化架构中复杂的亲和性调度"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:36
msgid ""
"**Decoupling**: Keeps inference instances independent without reporting "
"KV cache status to schedulers"
msgstr "**解耦**：保持推理实例独立，无需向调度器报告KV缓存状态"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:37
msgid ""
"**No Data Silos**: Centralized storage prevents redundant KV cache "
"accumulation across isolated instances"
msgstr "**无数据孤岛**：集中式存储防止跨隔离实例的冗余KV缓存积累"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/ucm_deployment.md:38
msgid ""
"**Better Compatibility**: Superior compatibility with PD disaggregation "
"and large-scale deployment"
msgstr "**更好的兼容性**：与PD分离和大规模部署具有卓越兼容性"

