"Cache Store (Device ↔ Host) and Posix Store (Host ↔ Storage backend) for "
"optimal transfer performance. For more configuration options, refer to "
"[UCM PipelineStore Documentation](https://ucm.readthedocs.io/en/latest"
"/user-guide/prefix-cache/pipeline_store.html)."
