"**注意**：PipelineStore是UCM推荐的连接器。它串联了Cache Store（设备↔主机）和Posix "
"Store（主机↔存储后端）以实现最佳传输性能。更多配置选项请参考[UCM "
"PipelineStore文档](https://ucm.readthedocs.io/en/latest/user-guide/prefix-"
"cache/pipeline_store.html)。"

